Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.61,0:01:33.57,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,いつからかな不思議
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.90,0:01:40.07,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,この胸の奥は 君の欠片ばかり
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.95,0:01:43.62,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you Do you trust me? Someday…please say Yes
